---
title: Summer Vegetable Salad with Seared Chicken, Garlic Croutons, and Mustard-Chive Vinaigrette
description: We’re nearing summer, but that doesn’t mean we’re ready to say goodbye to sweet peas, adorable baby carrots, and tender lettuces! This salad celebrates the best of early summer produce. Juicy pan-seared chicken and garlic croutons round out this hearty salad.
